name: After the Rain (iii)
description: After the Rain (iii) is part of a series of AI generated artworks exploring our relationship to technology and nature. In this series the viewer is taken on a journey through a landscape imagined by a machine. Unrestricted by the physical limitations of a human brain, an artificial neural network is able to ‘imagine’ shapes and forms that humans cannot. In this way the AI is able to create a vision of the natural world that is simultaneously familiar and uncanny.
